      "file_path": "reception/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/distribution/reception/parameters/PSSDConfigurationParametersGroup.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 156,
      "message": "I think this will not work as it generates new UUID every time. \nSo if you register this group in Parameter Service then you get one UUID. And when you try  fetching from Parameter Service by calling getName() method then the UUID will be different. That will lead to error.\n\nFor an instance of PSSDConfigurationParametersGroup, getName() should always return the same unique name.",
